BrightO, one of the ex-housemate of the fifth edition of the BBNaija tagged Lockdown edition, has revealed how he tipped Prince to win the show. In an open confession, BrightO told Ebuka, the show host, that aside himself, he had tipped Prince to win the BBNaija Lockdown edition. When queried why he tipped Prince after himself, he said: “I thought Prince will win the show after me because of his charisma and how he carried himself. He had the carriage of the possible winner and he was highly competitive. Earlier on in the show, BrightO, who was voted the biggest gossip in the house, had admitted telling Tochi that he didn’t see Prince dating Nengi because he couldn’t take on her financial demands.